         *    "mint is paused", so the exploit path's mint stage is infeasible there.
         * 2. `cFEI` is likewise mint-paused at this fork.
         * 3. `cUSDT`, `cTUSD`, and `cUSDP` remain mintable, but on-chain probes show no
         *    `cashDelta < mintAmount` shortfall, so they do not realize this finding in practice.
         */
        hypothesisRefuted = true;
    }

